{"tid":665922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[we7pay, 支爆pay]短片揭公安電腦監視用戶微信對話　高瑜：高科技公司是維穩工具","createTime":"2018-05-15T11:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T02:46:12.000Z","uid":51271,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"d56ed4084db482b0fa89c74b2a2e0793ed39e269","tid":665922,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T11:41:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E6%8F%AD%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1-%E9%AB%98%E7%91%9C-%E9%AB%98%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%98%AF%E7%B6%AD%E7%A9%A9%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%2591%259C-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E7%25A9%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25B7%2F&d=cppOGrXEjPmccJsJqcfD7ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=7c41c042\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%2585%25A6%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E5%25B0%258D%25E8%25A9%25B1-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%2591%259C-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E7%25A9%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%2585%25B7%2F&h=1bd2fbd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/china/%E7%9F%AD%E7%89%87%E6%8F%AD%E5%85%AC%E5%AE%89%E9%9B%BB%E8%85%A6%E7%9B%A3%E8%A6%96%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8D%E8%A9%B1-%E9%AB%98%E7%91%9C-%E9%AB%98%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%98%AF%E7%B6%AD%E7%A9%A9%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國著名獨立記者高瑜在Twitter發表一段影片，提到深圳南山區東安分局即當地的公安分局，設有騰訊取證中心，可以隨時調動出任何地區微信用戶的資料及相關用戶的資料。從片段可見，電腦可監察不同手機的現時微信情況及對話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/gaoyu200812/status/996333062882344961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgaoyu200812%2Fstatus%2F996333062882344961&d=cppOGrXEjPmccJsJqcfD7ozZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=37d8b5bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgaoyu200812%2Fstatus%2F996333062882344961&h=eb82bb83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/gaoyu200812/status/996333062882344961</a><br />\n<br />\n高瑜未有的帖文中提及片段的來源。她在帖文中稱，「警察國家，特務統治。高科技公司和老板都是維穩的工具和附庸。」即使個人將用戶資料刪除都沒用，因該該中心留有存底，並為公檢法辦案服務。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，高瑜提及的「深圳南山區東安分局」，是指深圳市公安局南山公安的分局，主管全區公安工作。騰訊去年遷入新公司總部，正位於深圳南山區高新科技園中的濱海大廈。"},{"pid":"7098ed44816c31324dae66822d3296af39f7814f","tid":665922,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T11:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/gao2-01_Wl2vm_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fgao2-01_Wl2vm_1200x0.png&h=03938121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8fec1de4c57299e2ae9d90ce6529f250ad71e0a","tid":665922,"uid":48083,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T11:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/194251_d3c024e3c52cfbf5e783f79dcef674ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F194251_d3c024e3c52cfbf5e783f79dcef674ae.png&h=af413079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" cl